title: FCC app 1.123:
message:
FCC app 1.123:
Updated graphs (removed back-fill and forward-fill, added points).
If value in table is greater than zero, but was rounded-down to 0.00 (e.g. 0.00499), ensure it is always plotted in the graph with a zero value.
Simplified menu options: re-ordered and simplified, to match that used in iOS.
The Settings screen now contains Clear All Results, Activation, and Configuration buttons.
The “Configuration” button takes you to the old System Info screen (AKA Preferences).
Moved the “Run Test” button to the top of the main screen, and generally tidied-up the layout of the top area in the main screen.
